data.description:
Welcome to your dream home! Located in lovely cul-de-sac, this exquisite brick and stone exterior residence is a testament to luxury living. From the moment you approach the custom glass front door, you'll be captivated by the meticulous attention to detail throughout the entire space. Beautiful wood trim, crown molding, and ornate designs adorn the interior, adding warmth and character to every room. This home boasts 3,108 square feet with 4 spacious bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, 1 half bath, 3 car garage, a storm shelter and ceiling fans throughout. 
The kitchen features granite countertops, abundant counter space, matching stainless steel appliances and a pantry with adorable decorative glass. 
The primary bedroom is a true retreat! The custom ceiling paintwork and the cozy fireplace really set the tone for peace and relaxation. The primary bathroom has a large double vanity, modern soaking tub, and standing shower. With access to a large closet, organizing your wardrobe is made easy! 
You’ll easily find your way upstairs when you spot the staircase with its beautiful custom carpet, leading you to a versatile bonus room with a closet and full bathroom. It can serve as a guest suite, home office, or recreation room. The laundry room is well-equipped with a sink, cabinets, counter space, and hanging areas for added convenience. Step outside to your beautifully landscaped backyard, complete with a covered patio and two ceiling fans. It's the perfect setting for outdoor gatherings, or al fresco dining.
This home truly exemplifies luxury living with its thoughtful design and high-end finishes. Whether you're entertaining in the spacious family room, relaxing in the primary suite, or enjoying your morning coffee under the backyard patio, every corner of this property exudes comfort and elegance.
